1. Install the dependencies in requirement.apt and the requirement.txt
2. Install python 3 from source code
3. Unlink the current python version and link with python3 version
4. Vrify python default version is python3. Execute python in cli to see the default version
5  GNS3 environment environment should be installed in the Test environment. GNS3 works on python3
6. Create the desired topolgy as per HAPPIEST_FRAMEWORK/Network_Protocol/BGP_OSPF/BGP_Topology.png
7. Edge core router with ONL OS having quagga router installed
8. Edit the BGP_OSPF/Topology_file.json and variables.py file
9. Start the test
   # cd HAPPIEST_FRAMEWORK/Network_Protocol/BGP_OSPF/
   # pybot BGP_OSPF_Test_with_GNS3.robot
